charge_types.content: Charging is possible by using a regular wall plug or a charging station. Public charging is always done through a charging station. How fast the EV can charge depends on the charging station (EVSE) used and the maximum charging capacity of the EV. The table below shows all possible options for charging the Mercedes-Benz EQE 300. Each option shows how fast the battery can be charged from empty to full.
charge_types.info: † = Limited by on-board charger, vehicle cannot charge faster.
